title: Australian notebook. No. 5
brief_description: Newsreel magazine containing the following items: 1. Albert Park Lake proves new attraction for weekend walkers 2. Agriculture Minister Chandler opens a tree-pruning demo at Burnley Horticultural Gardens 3. Labrador retrievers display ability in club trials at Templestowe 4. Fisheries and Game Department supervisors release 20,000 young trout in the Yarra River 5. Sports brief - Lacrosse at Malvern, hockey with Camberwell v Power House for Altona Cup.
